<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 15:15:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>梅赛德斯CEO：打破中国“信心危机”最重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-ceo-breaking-chinas-confidence-crisis-is-most-important-thing-2024-10-02/</link><description>梅赛德斯-奔驰首席执行官奥拉·康林松表示，结束中国消费者信心危机是梅赛德斯-奔驰中短期内最重要的事情，并将汽车市场描述为一场“达尔文之战”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:19:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-ceo-breaking-chinas-confidence-crisis-is-most-important-thing-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>小鹏汽车：我们来欧洲是为了带来技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-we-are-coming-europe-bring-technology-2024-10-02/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商小鹏汽车董事会副主席兼联席总裁布莱恩·顾表示，该汽车制造商不打算在欧洲销售其汽车以提供廉价替代品，而是为了带来自己的技术。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:12:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-we-are-coming-europe-bring-technology-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国将拨款高达 1 亿美元，以促进人工智能在半导体材料中的应用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-award-up-100-million-boost-use-ai-semiconductor-materials-2024-10-02/</link><description>美国商务部周三表示，计划拨款 1 亿美元，以促进人工智能在开发新型可持续半导体材料中的应用。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:06:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-award-up-100-million-boost-use-ai-semiconductor-materials-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔卡拉斯反击击败卫冕冠军辛纳夺得中国公开赛冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/alcaraz-fights-back-down-defending-champion-sinner-win-china-open-2024-10-02/</link><description>卡洛斯·阿尔卡拉斯在周三的中国公开赛决赛中，在先失一盘的情况下奋起直追，在决定性的抢七中顽强拼搏，以 6-7(6) 6-4 7-6(3) 击败卫冕冠军詹尼克·辛纳，夺得个人第四个网球冠军。季节。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:03:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/alcaraz-fights-back-down-defending-champion-sinner-win-china-open-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>马里诺队击败蔚山队，使亚冠联赛重回正轨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/marinos-put-asian-champions-league-campaign-back-track-with-ulsan-thrashing-2024-10-02/</link><description>横滨水手队周三从首日耻辱中恢复过来，在日本以 4-0 击败韩国蔚山 HD，让他们的亚洲冠军联赛精英赛重回正轨。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:49:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/marinos-put-asian-champions-league-campaign-back-track-with-ulsan-thrashing-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>通用汽车寻求在投资者日缓解股东的紧张情绪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-seeks-ease-shareholders-nerves-investor-day-2024-10-02/</link><description>投资者对汽车制造商的利润感到担忧，因为他们在电动汽车方面面临重大损失，燃气发动机汽车的销售陷入停滞，而且来自中国的压力不断加大。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-seeks-ease-shareholders-nerves-investor-day-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车呼吁德国投票反对欧盟对中国汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-calls-germany-vote-against-eu-tariffs-chinese-cars-2024-10-02/</link><description>大众汽车周三敦促德国投票反对欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税，称关税并不能提高汽车行业的竞争力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:30:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-calls-germany-vote-against-eu-tariffs-chinese-cars-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，欧盟的支持足以对中国电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/france-greece-italy-poland-set-back-chinese-ev-tariffs-sources-say-2024-10-02/</link><description>欧盟正在对中国制造的电动汽车进行反补贴调查，并已在周五投票之前向 27 个成员国发送了提案。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/france-greece-italy-poland-set-back-chinese-ev-tariffs-sources-say-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>德国肖尔茨呼吁与中国就电动汽车进行更多谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-scholz-talks-with-china-electric-vehicles-must-continue-2024-10-02/</link><description>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨周三表示，排除外国竞争并缩小贸易伙伴范围的做法是错误的，并表示必须继续与中国就电动汽车进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 11:30:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-scholz-talks-with-china-electric-vehicles-must-continue-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟要求 YouTube、Snapchat、TikTok 提供有关内容算法的信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-requests-information-youtube-snapchat-tiktok-about-recommendations-2024-10-02/</link><description>周三，欧盟委员会要求 YouTube、Snapchat 和 TikTok 提供信息，了解其算法向用户推荐内容所使用的参数，以及它们在放大一些系统性风险（包括与选举过程、心理健康和未成年人保护相关的风险）方面所扮演的角色。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:14:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-requests-information-youtube-snapchat-tiktok-about-recommendations-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中东紧张局势、港口罢工导致第四季度开局紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-02/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>2025年钻石联赛揭幕战两项赛事将在中国举办，决赛将在苏黎世举行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/china-host-opening-two-events-2025-diamond-league-final-zurich-2024-10-02/</link><description>组织者周三表示，苏黎世将于 8 月举行为期两天的 2025 年钻石联赛赛季决赛，比赛将在中国举行两场比赛。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:14:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/china-host-opening-two-events-2025-diamond-league-final-zurich-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，200多名中国公民从黎巴嫩撤离</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/more-than-200-chinese-citizens-evacuated-lebanon-state-media-says-2024-10-02/</link><description>据中国官方新华社周三报道，黎巴嫩政府已安全撤离200多名中国公民。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 08:54:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/more-than-200-chinese-citizens-evacuated-lebanon-state-media-says-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>即将离任的戴姆勒卡车首席执行官认为中国和德国没有复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/outgoing-daimler-truck-ceo-sees-no-recovery-china-germany-2024-10-02/</link><description>全球最大卡车制造商戴姆勒卡车即将卸任的首席执行官马丁·道姆 (Martin Daum) 在周二晚间的新闻发布会上表示，中国和德国卡车市场的复苏不会很快到来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 08:48:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/outgoing-daimler-truck-ceo-sees-no-recovery-china-germany-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>官员称，通过台湾海峡的德国船只已被警告驶离</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/german-ships-that-passed-through-taiwan-strait-were-warned-off-officials-say-2024-10-02/</link><description>德国特遣小组指挥官周三表示，上个月穿越台湾海峡的德国海军舰艇受到了中国船只的密切监视和重复无线电信息，但没有出现不安全行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:56:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/german-ships-that-passed-through-taiwan-strait-were-warned-off-officials-say-2024-10-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>